Package: neurofundata
Type: Package
Title: Functional data analysis tools for neuroimaging data.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Marco", "Palma", email = "M.Palma@warwick.ac.uk",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Marco Palma <M.Palma@warwick.ac.uk>
Description: This package is specifically designed to deal with 3-dimensional 
    images in NIfTI format and standard preprocessing tasks in neuroimaging.  
    It offers a suite of tools from functional data analysis (FDA) based on sparse arrays.
